title: Ep 149: The Laser Guy

description:
Dermatologist Robert Anolik, MD, is here to talk about Fraxel, IPL, LED, photorejuvenation, and all the laser things. We discuss how they work, the critical questions to ask before treatment, the products that complement treatment, and lots more. Before that: The college scandal rocks the beauty world, and Amazon launches its own private label skincare line.
